<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="167">Type material.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="167">
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="167">Holotype</emphasis>
: male, altitude 800 m, 9.VI.2017, Beibeng Village, Motuo County, Linzhi City, Xizang Autonomous Region, China, Zhao-hui Pan leg., slide STS-40151 (TAAHU). 
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="167">Paratypes</emphasis>
: 3 males, the same data as in the holotype, slides STS-40159, STS-40167 &amp; STS-40169 (TAAHU).
</paragraph>
